Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Tondo High School in the City of Manila to Aurelio V. Tolentino High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 795
An Act Changing the Name of the Tondo High School in the City of Manila to Aurelio V. Tolentino High School
Section 1. The name of the Tondo High School in the City of Manila is changed to Aurelio V. Tolentino High nynySchool.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
